{"type":"message","id":"4d2a82b1","parentId":"589c39cc","timestamp":"2026-04-01T21:48:50.090Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:3709e1d2-67b1-4eff-92e4-b586ec802978 空闲检测自主学习] 请检测当前是否有活跃对话（查询 sessions_list）。如果没有活跃对话（没有最近5分钟内的用户消息），则执行自主学习：\n\n1. 搜索企业数字化转型、智能安防、网络系统集成、IT运维服务等道简网络相关行业的最新动态\n2. 整理3-5条关键信息\n3. 保存到 /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md\n\n如果有活跃对话，直接回复\"检测到活跃对话，不执行自主学习\"\nCurrent time: Thursday, April 2nd, 2026 — 5:48 AM (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-04-01 21:48 UTC"}],"timestamp":1775080130087}}
{"type":"message","id":"3625cb48","parentId":"4d2a82b1","timestamp":"2026-04-01T21:48:56.158Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a cron job task. I need to:\n1. Check if there are active sessions (query sessions_list for recent messages within 5 minutes)\n2. If no active sessions, perform autonomous learning about industries related to 道简网络\n3. If active sessions exist, reply \"检测到活跃对话，不执行自主学习\"\n\nLet me first check sessions_list to see if there are any active conversations.","thinkingSignature":"5acdc248e5c1527b1acf044520f72ab02b7047ddc5dd0960e3cb8443a616c324"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_xjbi1oye69ae_1","name":"sessions_list","arguments":{"activeMinutes":5,"messageLimit":1}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":137,"output":121,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":172,"totalTokens":44411,"cost":{"input":0.000041099999999999996,"output":0.0001452,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0.00002064,"total":0.0015263699999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775080130088}}
